official_title: An Educational Video's Impact on Knowledge About HPV Vaccination and Cervical Cancer Screening Among Hispanic Patients: a Randomized Control Trial
inclusion_criteria:
* Female patient
* Hispanic patients
* Between age 21-65 y/o
* Receiving pap smear during clinic appointment
Healthy volunteers allowed
Must be FEMALE
Must have minimum age of 21 Years
Must have maximum age of 65 Years
exclusion_criteria:
* Non-female patients
* Non-Hispanic patients
* Age less than 21
* Age greater than 65
* not receiving pap smear
